Your directories are all screwed up.

You need to start with a working simple JUnit / Cobertura example
project and then add your files or modify until it suits your needs.
Cutting and pasting from webpages into a build.xml file is not
necessarily going to work.

You need to start with a working Cobertura project and then remove
their source code, add yours, and try again.

Wayne

